Fort Allbritton was a new member at that time. All 
right, let's back up to coeducate. Fort

00:11.099 --> 00:15.966
Allbritton was on in 73, because he was the one that 
was in particular. When the proposal about

00:16.326 --> 00:23.336
coeducation, non-compulsory core came up, do you 
have any idea what Mr. Rudder's initial reaction

00:23.396 --> 00:25.880
was? Do you have any idea whether he was for it or 
not? Well, I would say Mr. Rudder probably

00:31.983 --> 00:35.327
wouldn't have expressed his initial reaction. I 
think Mr. Rudder's documentary is going to think

